For High School Seniors
Class of 2020
(Ballico Alumni)

With the current school closures, Ballico Cressey PTC Scholarship applications can be emailed to

Megan Schwall at schwall.m@ballicocressey.com
or mailed to
12481 Bradbury Road Ballico, 95303.

If you choose to mail your application it must be postmarked by April 10th. Emailed applications must be sent/received by the end of the day on April 10th. A sealed transcript is not required if you are emailing your application.

WOOHOO - A HUGE THANK YOU!! Thanks to everyone who donated trees @ Cressey and Ballico. Ed Hickman and his guys planted more trees @ Cressey this weekend, around our play structure . ( I think that's about 40 new trees total on our campus). We also had some magical folks sneak in and paint a bunch of sidewalk games for our little people. You should of heard the kids and staff delight as they entered campus!. "Trees!!" "Look Look !!"
This type of community support and care is why I am so very proud to be a part of this school and our families.
Again, THANK YOU - Mr.B : Principal #cresseyconquers #ballicobraves
